card.title: myuhc.com helps you manage your plan online

text.text: myuhc.com is the gateway to your benefits and claims information. You can view your own personalized plan information, choices for where to go for care, budgeting tools, helpful wellness tips, and more.

card_944372199.title: UnitedHealthcare® app helps you manage your plan on your phone

text.text: Whether you need to find urgent care, forgot your health plan ID card, or need to call Customer Care, the UnitedHealthcare® app helps put insurance information in the palm of your hand.
